{"tid":1785314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我見啲節目成日介紹英文啲idiom、slang同phrasal verb","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T01:45:44.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c662c3cc621e2458514995b3742e925f62538f64","tid":1785314,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:38:24.000Z","msg":"其實呢啲嘢常唔常用o架？使用頻率係高定低？<br />\n去到外國啲人係咪全部都識都知我講呢啲嘢嘅意思？<br />\n同埋如果喺香港用呢啲嘢啲人會唔會唔明或者覺得我作狀？<br />\n如果喺香港啲英文writing paper用呢啲嘢啲英文改卷老師會唔會唔明？定係都要查字典先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2908c38a7c40169954fa89a527c662d42a259b","tid":1785314,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人知？"},{"pid":"9aac24b83a89fb027adde79766eeaec10acd8803","tid":1785314,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"有冇 examples"},{"pid":"9c7e7b0a837de47ec353ae0d50a4c14ff9085fa3","tid":1785314,"uid":235911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"當年ce 作文，背咗啲idiom 寫落去，最後A 咗。當然要純熟運用。"},{"pid":"9eac2244e14758c86673df67f07d4b19cdaa72a1","tid":1785314,"uid":235911,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:26:49.000Z","msg":"唔駛要好深，要夠貼地。<br />\neg No bees，no honey。No work，no money。"},{"pid":"de432d97c61c60e70a1638d4552df2fa35a75fc0","tid":1785314,"uid":152759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"真係明意思 又真係岩用先好用 唔好抱住加落去好似會勁啲咁既心態去用 最緊要自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1cdc1d9b48668244e39703d4a5daff03bfee78","tid":1785314,"uid":262093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"我諗同我哋用廣東話一樣，idiom唔常用，但講出嚟會顯得好機鋒，我哋呢一代識嘅揭後語已經少過上一代好多，唔知下一代仲有幾多人識。<br />\n<br />\nSlang嘅話壽命短週期快用嘅人未必多，但識用會好快融入人哋。你唔會期望外國人識講「hea」「蛇齋餅稯」「大白象」，但如果佢哋識嘅話你未必會當佢外國人。<br />\n<br />\nPhrasal verb有啲似廣東話嘅動補詞「打開」、「拎起」、「做完」，亦都有啲似日文嘅「取り上げる(拎起、褫奪)」、「話しかける(搭訕)」，簡言之係除咗動詞外仲有狀態。如果語境令你唔止要講動作仲要強調物件狀態嘅話，都係用下比較好，而且對我嚟講英文phrasal verb會比單一動詞入屋啲，如果唔係會顯得好有學問或正式。例如日常對話，比起「being assimilated」，「blend in」會好啲；比起「continue」，「carry on」會好啲。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係native，以上只係綜合我學語言嘅經驗。"},{"pid":"ec2dc71e0e98bd7791f704091f367e1db2612e25","tid":1785314,"uid":262093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"可以試下如果有個學緊廣東話嘅外國人問一樣嘅問題，你會點答。"},{"pid":"b7c7686c10cbda2dbfb4709f0a1bd79ddbb116b7","tid":1785314,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"睇劇 就成日有講 <br />\nidiom ， phrasal verb"},{"pid":"edde2764cccdb481fecb5b955b305c7bfea1e853","tid":1785314,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2dc71e0e98bd7791f704091f367e1db2612e25","tid":1785314,"uid":262093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"可以試下如果有個學緊廣東話嘅外國人問一樣嘅問題，你會點答。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"如果唔識， 其實係溝通唔到"},{"pid":"8cf58a4eb481eb3ac55c6a84aadf4fa9f59a13ff","tid":1785314,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edde2764cccdb481fecb5b955b305c7bfea1e853","tid":1785314,"uid":67692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2dc71e0e98bd7791f704091f367e1db2612e25","tid":1785314,"uid":262093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:48:10.000Z","msg":"可以試下如果有個學緊廣東話嘅外國人問一樣嘅問題，你會點答。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:27:46.000Z","msg":"如果唔識， 其實係溝通唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"識嘅多數都老人家，好似我識嘅廣東話諺語肯定比我老豆老母嘅少，phrasal verb都可以睇字面估到？"},{"pid":"3e2598c880c8fa39ed58b54d08cb9e37acfb32ca","tid":1785314,"uid":67692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"終於俾我搵到 有本書 專講slang<br />\n呢d至係生活英文<br />\n